for cind in np.arange(len(self.ms.colors)):
    vals = self.ms.getFloatData(self.ms.colorstr[cind])
    goodinds = np.isfinite(vals)
    self.assertTrue(np.all(self.ms.TeffColor(self.ms.colors[cind][0], self.
        ms.colors[cind][1], self.ms.Teff[goodinds]) == vals[goodinds]), 
        'Cannot reproduce colors from interpolant for %s' % self.ms.
        colorstr[cind])
